_sText: This Map is a Bomb/defuse map. Bomb zone is at the very top of the map. There is a weak spot in the wall that you can shoot through and if you fall down there you won't die. Just go into the tele up against the wall were the arrow points and u will spawn on top of what looks like invisable flooring. go on to the wood part and there is 2 invisable ladders you can clime up and plant the bomb. There is also 2 tele's in opposite corners of the map were it spawns u on a platform and u can snipe ppl from there.Secret tele's all over going to cool spots all over the map.
